Package: sumsamstats
Type: Package
Title: Summarizing Samtools Stats Output With ATAC-seq QC in mind 
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Maciek", "Migda≈Ç", email = "mcjmigdal@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <mcjmigdal@gmail.com>
Description: The package provides samtools stats parser that allows to easly read stats report to R. It also provides several plotting functions for quick visualisation of libraries statistics. Can be used to create summaries and allow quick inspection of multiple samples. Available plots were done as so they allow to check some of the ENCODE ATAC-seq quality guidelines.
